{"EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:0000": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Blood moon?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:0001": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "I've seen it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:0002": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Good-bye."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:1000": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Blood moon?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:1001": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Tonight's moon?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:1002": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Good-bye."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:BloodyMoon00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [1, 11]}}, {"text": "Whenever the clock strikes midnight on\nunlucky nights, the sky turns blood red.\nThat's the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ".\nWhen that happens, "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "monsters"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " come back\nto life, no matter how many times you've\ndefeated them.\nIt's happened for so long now that no\none really pays it any mind, but I have no\nplans to give up on my research."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:BloodyTalk00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [7, 10]}}, {"text": "It's...so...RED!\nSo gloriously RED!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:BloodyTalk01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [7, 36]}}, {"text": "My blood...it's boiling!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:BloodyTalk02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [7, 10]}}, {"text": "Arise, monsters!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:BloodyTalk03": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [8, 36]}}, {"text": "Gr...gr...gr..."}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 16]}}, {"text": "Hmm..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [4, 19]}}, {"text": "Oh, sorry...\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "I didn't notice you... I was a bit lost in\nthought there."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk01_1": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "What's up?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"text": "I've been doing rigorous research day\nand night to figure out the mystery of \nthat "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [0, 1, 2], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk03": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [4, 20]}}, {"text": "You don't know it?\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "That's inexcusable. Listen up and I'll tell\nyou about it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk04": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 6]}}, {"text": "Hmmm..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": " Are you just pretending to\nknow what I was talking about?\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "That's fine, so long as you'll listen to me\nnow while I tell you about it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk05": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "Hmm..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nAll the same, take a minute and listen\nwhile I tell you about it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk06": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "For 100 years now, every so often when\nthe clock strikes midnight, the sky turns\nred and a full moon rises...\nAt that moment, "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "monsters"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " that had been\npreviously defeated will come back\nto life."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk07": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [7, 11]}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"text": "And that's what is known as the\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:FirstTalk08": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "Why do the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "monsters"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " return to life? "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nWhy does it only happen when the sky\nturns red?\nNo one really has the answers to those\nquestions. It's a mysterious\nphenomenon...\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [1, 11]}}, {"text": "If you learn anything about the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood\nmoon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " as you travel, be sure to come\nback and tell me."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:GoodBye00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 16]}}, {"text": "Hmm...\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [4, 1]}}, {"text": "Oh, I'm sorry...\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "I spend so much time thinking about the\nmoon that it's all I can talk about."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:GoodBye01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 16]}}, {"text": "Hmm..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [1, 11]}}, {"text": "Tonight is the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ", at last..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon00_After": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 0]}}, {"text": "The "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon "}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "has come and gone.\nTime to start waiting for the next one..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon00_Befor": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 16]}}, {"text": "I'm getting that feeling again..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nSomething is going to happen tonight."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nI can taste it!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon00_Full": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is a full moon...\n\n\nLooks like it could come falling down any\nminute. I can't take my eyes off of it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight's moon will be a little smaller\nthan yesterday's full moon. It's nice in\nits own way, really..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is the third-quarter moon."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "\nLike a bow aiming for the heavens above."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon03": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is the 26th-day moon..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nIts sloping line is really wonderful."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon04": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is a new moon..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nEven though we can't see it, isn't it\ngreat just knowing it's there?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon05": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is a crescent moon..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "\nThat shape makes me hungry for some\nreason..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon06": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is a seven-day moon...\nLike a bow aiming for the land below,\nit really is quite beautiful."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Moon07": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "Tonight is the 13th-day moon..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nNow it will slowly expand. So beautiful..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [14, 205]}}, {"text": "Hmm..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"text": "ZZZzzz..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [14, 205]}}, {"text": "Tonight..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near03": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [10, 205]}}, {"text": "Rain..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near04": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"text": "Rain!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near05": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [32, 205]}}, {"text": "I'm sleeping..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near06": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [8, 205]}}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "BLOOD!"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Near07": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound2", "unknown": [8, 205]}}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "Here...it...COMES!"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Rain00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "Hmm..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": " Can't see the moon like this."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Rain01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "I'm taking cover from the rain!\nWe'll talk later!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Rain02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "Can't see anything in this rain!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk00": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 0]}}, {"text": "Oh, you again...\nAre you interested in my research?"}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk01": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 0]}}, {"text": "Well, ask me anything."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk02": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 0]}}, {"text": "Oh, you again."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nThe moon is about to come out..."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk03": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [1, 11]}}, {"text": "Oh, you again."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nA beautiful moon tonight, isn't it?"}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk03_1": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [10, 21]}}, {"text": "Oh..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": " You were researching the\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "blood moon"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ", as well?"}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk04": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "Oh...\nIt looks like the moon has already\ndisappeared today..."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk05": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "Anything else you want to ask?"}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk06": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "What is it? I was just about to get some\nsleep so I can be rested for researching\nthe moon tonight..."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_SouthHateru007:Talk07": {"attributes": "Npc_SouthHateru007", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [3, 12]}}, {"text": "What is it? I was just sleeping so I'd be\nwell rested for researching the moon\ntonight..."}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [1000, 1001, 1002], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 2, "unknown": 8}}]}}